---
import MarketingLayout from '../../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro';
---
<MarketingLayout title="Process | Website Factory" description="How intake, build, review, and launch work.">
  <section class="content-section"><div class="container prose">
    <h1>Process</h1>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Intake:</strong> You provide business details, services, photos, and goals.</li>
      <li><strong>Build:</strong> We produce copy and design using the best-fit template style.</li>
      <li><strong>Review:</strong> You approve and request focused revisions.</li>
      <li><strong>Launch:</strong> We deploy to Cloudflare Pages, Netlify, or GitHub Pages.</li>
    </ol>
  </div></section>
</MarketingLayout>
